<template>
     <b-form-group>
        <label :for="unique">{{ label }}</label>
        <!-- <b-form-input type="number" :id="unique" v-model="value" @input="$emit('updated', value)" :placeholder="placeholder"></b-form-input> -->
        <vue-slider type="number" :id="unique" v-model="value" :mix="18" :max="120" @input="$emit('updated', value)" :placeholder="placeholder"></vue-slider>

// import { EventBus } from './event-bus.js';
import VueSlider from 'vue-slider-component'
import 'vue-slider-component/theme/default.css'

export default {
     props: {
            label: String,
            unique: String,
            placeholder: Number,
    },
    components:{
        VueSlider
    },
    data () {
        return {
            value: '',
        }
    }
}
</script>
<style scoped>
.form-group{
    margin: 20px !important;
}
label {
    margin-right: 5px;
}
